        "message": "Patch Set 4:\n\n(12 comments)\n\nthere are a lot of repeated (or similar) code blocks here, both in the test code and in the production code.  That implies that we should refactor some of these data structures so that the common stuff is in a superclass and then the common parts of these similar methods could be moved to the superclass.  Maybe create a JIRA for Jakarta to do some refactoring.",
